# Task Pet Simulator 🐾📝

A C++ CLI application that combines task management with a virtual pet. Complete tasks to level up your pet!

**University Project**  
*Course: CSC 327*  
*Developed by: Taylor Carver, Franissa Simon, Javid Hanmore, Conner Garris*

---

## Features
- 🐶 Create and customize a virtual pet (name, type)
- ✅ Add/view/complete/delete tasks
- ⚡ Earn EXP for your pet by completing tasks
- 📈 Level up your pet (IQ, Love, Level stats)
- 💾 Save/load progress to/from local files
- 🔄 Reset all data

## Prerequisites
- C++17 compiler (e.g., g++ 9.0+)
- Standard Library Filesystem support

## Installation
1. Clone the repo:
   ```bash
   git clone https://github.com/T707C/T707C-StudentPetSimulator-MidSemester-Project.git


## To Run
" ./taskpet "
